net.hudup.core.parser

Interface DatasetParser

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Alg, AlgRemote, DatasetParserRemote, java.util.EventListener, Exportable, java.rmi.Remote, java.io.Serializable, SetupAlgListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DatasetParserAbstract, DatasetParserRemoteWrapper, DbServerIndicator, FlatServerIndicator, Indicator, JesterjokeParser, KBaseIndicator, MovielensParser, NullIndicator, RmiServerIndicator, ScannerParser, ScannerParserImpl, SemiScannerParser, SemiScannerParserExt, SnapshotParser, SnapshotParserImpl, SocketServerIndicator

    public interface DatasetParser
extends DatasetParserRemote, Alg
    DatasetParser is one of main interface responsible for reading and parsing coarse data such as CSV file, Excel file, database table into Dataset. The main method of DatasetParser is DatasetParserRemote.parse(DataConfig) that receives the input as configuration of data source and returns the output as a Dataset. For example, in order to parse Movielens data, programmers often create a MovielensParser which is an implementation of this interface DatasetParser and then, define the method DatasetParserRemote.parse(DataConfig) according to features of Movielens data.
    Version:
    10.0
    Author:
    Loc Nguyen
